rk&page_title=AI Risk Management Framework&source_entity_type=node&source_entity_id=1674601\"}]}"}],"structuredContent":{"success":true,"cached":false,"url":"https://www.nist.gov/itl/ai-risk-management-framework","title":"AI Risk Management Framework | NIST","content":"[![Circular design includes elements of the AI Risk Management Framework: Govern, Measure, Manage, Map.](/sites/default/files/styles/thumbnail/public/images/2023/01/25/RMF-redesign-rounded-other_graphics-04.png?itok=q6XNzk9H)](/news-events/news/2023/01/nist-risk-management-framework-aims-improve-trustworthiness-artificial)\n\nNew guidance seeks to cultivate trust in AI technologies and promote AI innovation while mitigating risk.","content_length":431,"links":[{"text":"Skip to main content","url":"https://www.nist.gov/itl/ai-risk-management-framework#main-content"},{"text":"Information Technology Laboratory","url":"https://www.nist.gov/itl"},{"text":"Download the AI RMF 1.0","url":"https://nvlpubs.nist.gov/nistpubs/ai/NIST.AI.100-1.pdf"},{"text":"View the AI RMF Playbook","url":"https://airc.nist.gov/airmf-resources/playbook/"},{"text":"Visit the AI Resource Center","url":"https://airc.nist.gov/"},{"text":"NIST AI Risk Management Framework (AI RMF)","url":"https://doi.org/10.6028/NIST.AI.100-1"},{"text":"workshops","url":"https://www.nist.gov/artificial-intelligence/nist-ai-engagement"},{"text":"Fact Sheet","url":"https://www.nist.gov/document/about-nist-ai-rmf"},{"text":"NIST AI RMF Playbook","url":"https://airc.nist.gov/AI_RMF_Knowledge_Base/Playbook"},{"text":"AI RMF Roadmap","url":"https://www.nist.gov/itl/ai-risk-management-framework/roadmap-nist-artificial-intelligence-risk-management-framework-ai"},{"text":"AI RMF Crosswalk","url":"https://www.nist.gov/itl/ai-risk-management-framework/crosswalks-nist-artificial-intelligence-risk-management-framework"},{"text":"Perspectives","url":"https://www.nist.gov/itl/ai-risk-management-framework/perspectives-about-nist-artificial-intelligence-risk-management"},{"text":"Trustworthy and Responsible AI Resource Center","url":"https://airc.nist.gov/Home"},{"text":"AIRC’s Use Case page","url":"https://airc.nist.gov/Usecases"},{"text":"NIST-AI-600-1, Artificial Intelligence Risk Management Framework: Generative Artificial Intelligence","url":"https://doi.org/10.6028/NIST.AI.600-1"},{"text":"AI RMF Development","url":"https://www.nist.gov/itl/ai-risk-management-framework/ai-rmf-development"},{"text":"NIST AI Risk Management Framework","url":"https://nvlpubs.nist.gov/nistpubs/ai/NIST.AI.100-1.ara.pdf"},{"text":"NIST AI Risk Management Framework","url":"https://nvlpubs.nist.gov/nistpubs/ai/NIST.AI.100-1.jpn.pdf"},{"text":"Second draft of the AI Risk Management Framework","url":"https://www.nist.gov/document/ai-risk-management-framework-2nd-draft"},{"text":"Initial draft of the AI Risk Management Framework","url":"https://www.nist.gov/document/ai-risk-management-framework-initial-draft"},{"text":"Concept paper to help guide development of the AI Risk Management Framework","url":"https://www.nist.gov/document/airmfconceptpaper"},{"text":"Brief summary","url":"https://www.nist.gov/document/summary-analysis-responses-nist-artificial-intelligence-risk-management-framework-ai-rmf"},{"text":"responses","url":"https://www.nist.gov/itl/ai-risk-management-framework/comments-received-rfi-artificial-intelligence-risk-management"},{"text":"Draft -Taxonomy of AI Risk","url":"https://www.nist.gov/document/draft-taxonomy-ai-risk-october-15-2021"},{"text":"AI Risk Management Framework Request for Information","url":"https://www.federalregister.gov/documents/2021/07/29/2021-16176/artificial-intelligence-risk-management-framework"},{"text":"Was this page helpful?","url":"https://www.nist.gov/webform/page_feedback?page=https://www.nist.gov/itl/ai-risk-management-framework&page_title=AI Risk Management Framework&source_entity_type=node&source_entity_id=1674601"}]},"isError":false},"toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01B8sswHA79jwkApUVcF3n13","executionTimeM