ecurity-compliance-platform/"},{"text":"follow him in LinkedIn here","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/maxaulakh/"},{"text":"5 Reasons Why Organizations Don’t Achieve FedRAMP ATO","url":"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/reasons-organizations-fedramp-ato/"},{"text":"Single-Tenant vs Multi-Tenant FedRAMP Deployments","url":"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/single-tenant-multi-tenant/"},{"text":"What Happens If You Lose Your FedRAMP Authorization?","url":"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/what-happens-lose-fedramp/"}]},"isError":false},"toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01VZ9Wg2fMyyTekcmygAZrcu","executionTimeMs":316,"targetServer":"openagentic_web","timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:27:43.996Z"}

