orm-still-a-viable-tool-for-fedramp-compliance\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"a pilot program called 20x\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/fedramp-20x-phase-one/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"the eligibility and requirements can be found here\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.fedramp.gov/20x/phase-two/participate/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"checking it directly on the 20x page\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.fedramp.gov/20x/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Significant Change Notification\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.fedramp.gov/rfcs/0007/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"the now-defunct P-ATO process\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/what-fedramp-jab-process/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"ConMon\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/conmon-fedramp-continuous-monitoring/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"release 5.2.0\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://csrc.nist.gov/pubs/sp/800/53/r5/upd1/final\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"schedule a call to see it in action and get started\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/cybersecurity-compliance-platform/#Book-your-Demo-Today\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Max Aulakh\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/author/ignyte/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"United States Air Force\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.amu.apus.edu/aboutus/meet-our-students/amu-max-aulakh/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Ignyte Assurance Platform\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/cybersecurity-compliance-platform/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"follow him in LinkedIn here\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/maxaulakh/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"5 Reasons Why Organizations Don’t Achieve FedRAMP ATO\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/reasons-organizations-fedramp-ato/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Single-Tenant vs Multi-Tenant FedRAMP Deployments\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/single-tenant-multi-tenant/\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"What Happens If You Lose Your FedRAMP Authorization?\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/what-happens-lose-fedramp/\\\"}]}\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"structuredContent\": {\n    \"success\": true,\n    \"cached\": false,\n    \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/\",\n    \"title\": \"What New Changes Are Coming to FedRAMP in 2026?\",\n    \"content\": \"### [5 Reasons Why Organizations Don’t Achieve FedRAMP ATO](https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/reasons-organizations-fedramp-ato/)\\n\\nJanuary 23, 2026\",\n    \"content_length\": 157,\n    \"links\": [\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Skip to content\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#content\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Max Aulakh\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/author/ignyte/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"PublishedDecember 12, 2025\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/2025/12/12/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"the FedRAMP Authorization Act\",\n        \"url\": \"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"M-24-15\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.fedramp.gov/resources/documents/FedRAMP_Policy_Memo.pdf\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"The Big News: More FedRAMP 20x\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#the-big-news-more-fedramp-20x\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"What Does FedRAMP 20x Phase 2 Entail?\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#what-does-fedramp-20x-phase-2-entail\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Will There Be a FedRAMP 20x Phase 3 Trial?\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#will-there-be-a-fedramp-20x-phase-3-trial\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"What Else is Happening in 2026?\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#what-else-is-happening-in-2026\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"From Significant Change Requests to Significant Change Notifications\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#from-significant-change-requests-to-significant-change-notifications\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Implementing the Minimum Assessment Standard\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#implementing-the-minimum-assessment-standard\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Better Reciprocity with Authorized Data Sharing\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#better-reciprocity-with-authorized-data-sharing\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Enhanced Requirements for Continuous Monitoring\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#enhanced-requirements-for-continuous-monitoring\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Recommended Secure Configurations\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#recommended-secure-configurations\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Aggressive Iteration and Rapid Development\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#aggressive-iteration-and-rapid-development\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Additional Questions About FedRAMP in 2026\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#additional-questions-about-fedramp-in-2026\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Are there any plans to update NIST SP 800-53 in 2026?\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#are-there-any-plans-to-update-nist-sp-800-53-in-2026\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Will FedRAMP itself see another major version update?\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#will-fedramp-itself-see-another-major-version-update\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Is the Ignyte Assurance Platform still a viable tool for FedRAMP compliance?\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/new-changes-fedramp-2026/#is-the-ignyte-assurance-platform-still-a-viable-tool-for-fedramp-compliance\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"a pilot program called 20x\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/fedramp-20x-phase-one/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"the eligibility and requirements can be found here\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.fedramp.gov/20x/phase-two/participate/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"checking it directly on the 20x page\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.fedramp.gov/20x/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Significant Change Notification\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.fedramp.gov/rfcs/0007/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"the now-defunct P-ATO process\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/what-fedramp-jab-process/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"ConMon\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/conmon-fedramp-continuous-monitoring/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"release 5.2.0\",\n        \"url\": \"https://csrc.nist.gov/pubs/sp/800/53/r5/upd1/final\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"schedule a call to see it in action and get started\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/cybersecurity-compliance-platform/#Book-your-Demo-Today\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Max Aulakh\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/author/ignyte/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"United States Air Force\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.amu.apus.edu/aboutus/meet-our-students/amu-max-aulakh/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Ignyte Assurance Platform\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/cybersecurity-compliance-platform/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"follow him in LinkedIn here\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/in/maxaulakh/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"5 Reasons Why Organizations Don’t Achieve FedRAMP ATO\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/reasons-organizations-fedramp-ato/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"Single-Tenant vs Multi-Tenant FedRAMP Deployments\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/single-tenant-multi-tenant/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"text\": \"What Happens If You Lose Your FedRAMP Authorization?\",\n        \"url\": \"https://www.ignyteplatform.com/blog/fedramp/what-happens-lose-fedramp/\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"isError\": false\n}","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01VZ9Wg2fMyyTekcmygAZrcu","timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:27:54.779Z","source":"database","confirmed":true}

